1. *Pakla* je vatra u kaminu. (The *fireplace* is on fire.)
2. Molim te donesi mi *paklu* cigareta. (Please bring me a *pack* of cigarettes.)
3. Mesar mi je dao komad *paklene* kobasice. (The butcher gave me a piece of *spicy* sausage.)
4. Moramo da popravimo *paklenu* situaciju u firmi. (We need to fix the *disastrous* situation in the company.)
5. *Paklom* je premazao dasku pre nego što je počeo da seče meso. (He coated the board with *lard* before starting to cut the meat.)
6. *Paklov* je pogled uputio prema meni kad sam mu rekla loše vesti. (He gave me a *sinister* look when I told him the bad news.)
7. Nekoliko radnika je dobilo otkaze zbog *paklenog* tempa rada. (Several employees were fired due to the *hellish* pace of work.)
8. *Pakleni* plan je bio da ukrade novac i nestane u inostranstvo. (The *devilish* plan was to steal money and disappear abroad.)
9. Na ulici smo videli grupu momaka kako se igraju *paklenog* fudbala. (We saw a group of boys playing *intense* football on the street.)
10. Kupio sam novi *paklarski* alat za posao. (I bought a new *fitter's* tool for work.)